SweepDock is an unofficial macOS desktop wrapper for the Mole CLI.

It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by the Mole project or its
author. Mole is developed by tw93:

https://github.com/tw93/Mole

Mole and related official product names, logos, and branding belong to their
respective owners. SweepDock does not include Mole source code and invokes the
locally installed `mo` command-line executable.

Because Mole is distributed under GPL-3.0 and this project is designed to work
with that ecosystem, SweepDock is published under GPL-3.0-compatible terms.
